    (comment 1 "Top-Level Hierarchical Sheet")
    (comment 2 "1800W Induction Heating System")
  )

  (lib_symbols)

  (text "TEMPER INDUCTION COOKER\n\nHierarchical Design Overview\n\nPower Flow:\nAC Mains (120V) → Voltage Doubler → DC Bus (340V)\n                 → Half-Bridge → Resonant Tank → Coil\n\nControl Flow:\nESP32-S3 → PWM → Gate Driver → IGBTs\n        ← ADC ← CT Sensing\n        ← SPI ← Temperature Sensing\n\nSafety:\nOCP + OVP + Thermal + Watchdog → SHUTDOWN_N\n\nPower Rails:\n+3.3V (MCU, Logic)\n+15V (Gate Driver, Safety Logic)\n+5V (Isolated Sensors)"
    (exclude_from_sim no)
